# Validation Tests

## 1. DHCP Verification

Command:
ipconfig /all

Expected:
- IP address in 172.16.0.x range
- DNS: 172.16.0.10
- Gateway: 172.16.0.10

---

## 2. Domain Join

Test:
System joined to domain: lab.local

Expected:
Login with domain account works

